r sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.\n\t\t","en_US":"Iris Eyewear is charting a new course for 2025, anticipating a surge in personalized, sustainable eyewear. Their latest collection blends cutting-edge 3D-printed frames with bio-acetate, reflecting a commitment to both style and environmental responsibility. Expect to see vibrant, customizable color palettes and modular designs that adapt to individual lifestyles. Iris is also embracing augmented reality, allowing retailers to offer virtual try-ons, enhancing the customer experience. By focusing on innovation and sustainability, Iris is not just following trends, but setting them, reshaping the future of eyewear.","config":{"mapperType":"link"}},"card-title":{"defaultValue":"Card title","en_US":"Visionary Shifts: How Iris Optical is Redefining Eyewear Trends for 2025.","config":{"mapperType":"link"}},"card-link":{"defaultValue":"Read more","config":{"mapperType":"link","href":"#"}},"category":{"defaultValue":"\n\t\t\tcategory\n\t\t","en_US":"","config":{"mapperType":"link"}}}}','nyap',1,NULL,1,'2026-04-27 16:34:32.151000',NULL)
